   "source": [
    "# ChuckleNet Phase C — Theory of Mind Fusion\n",
    "\n",
    "**Goal**: Combine three modalities to fix WavLM's precision gap:\n",
    "\n",
    "| Branch | Model | Test F1 | Role |\n",
    "|--------|-------|---------|------|\n",
    "| **Text** | XLM-R (frozen) | 0.8194 | Semantic incongruity detection |\n",
    "| **Audio** | WavLM (partial unfreeze) | ~0.62 | Acoustic laughter patterns |\n",
    "| **Prosody-ToM** | Pause/F0/RMS features | ~0.14 (weak alone) | Conversational timing signals |\n",
    "\n",
    "**Key insight from Purandare 2006**: Pause >0.8s BEFORE punchline is the single most validated acoustic humor signal. Not detectable from text. Extractable from audio.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Architecture**:\n",
    "```\n",
    "Text: XLM-R([CLS]) → 768-dim → linear(768→256) → text_emb\n",
    "Audio: WavLM(5s audio) → mean-pool → 768-dim → linear(768→256) → audio_emb\n",
    "Prosody: [pause_max, pause_density, f0_stats, rms_stats] → linear(52→64) → prosody_emb\n",
    "Fused: concat([text_emb, audio_emb, prosody_emb]) → MLP(256+256+64 → 128 → 2)\n",
    "```"
   ]
  },
